{
  "id": "6a2130843edfc4dd9223a26c",
  "title": "helpfeel/cosense-cliを試す",
  "created": 1780560007,
  "updated": 1780565202,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2130843edfc4dd9223a26c",
      "text": "helpfeel/cosense-cliを試す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560007,
      "updated": 1780560007
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21308f00000000004d406d",
      "text": "[helpfeel/cosense-cli]を試す[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560007,
      "updated": 1780560030
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130d200000000004d407b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560072,
      "updated": 1780560072
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130a300000000004d4073",
      "text": "環境",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560026,
      "updated": 1780560028
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130a800000000004d4074",
      "text": " [OpenCode], [Kimi K2.6]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560031,
      "updated": 1780560032
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130aa00000000004d4075",
      "text": " [scrapbox-userscript-std]のrepoがあるdirectoryで実行",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560032,
      "updated": 1780560044
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130c900000000004d4079",
      "text": " prompt",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560064,
      "updated": 1780560068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130b600000000004d4076",
      "text": "  $ https://github.com/helpfeel/cosense-cli を使ってみたいが、OpenCodeでこれを使えるだろうか？milestoneは、cosense-cliもしくはそれに類似する仕組みを使って、scrapbox-userscript-stdに関してscrapbox.io/takkerに書き込まれているページを編集し、今後の実装方針などを立てていくこと。",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560044,
      "updated": 1780560068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130c500000000004d4078",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560060,
      "updated": 1780560070
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130cf00000000004d407a",
      "text": "さすがにOpenCode向けのpluginは提供されていないのですぐには使えなかったが、よしなに解釈してやってくれそうな雰囲気はしている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560070,
      "updated": 1780560104
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21309600000000004d406f",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/4cda7f33e38ba2e55c2d833135031966]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560012,
      "updated": 1780560013
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2130f600000000004d407d",
      "text": "PATを発行して渡す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560108,
      "updated": 1780560112
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21309700000000004d4070",
      "text": "`~/.cosense/settings.json`を作ってそこにPATを置く案を提案してくれた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560013,
      "updated": 1780560484
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21326d00000000004d407e",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/db9011d4f9e1cbd046e4811c7bbfe997]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560484,
      "updated": 1780560485
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21326e00000000004d407f",
      "text": "subagentsが起動してなんか作業し始めた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560485,
      "updated": 1780560586
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2132d200000000004d4080",
      "text": " OpenCodeでsubagentが起動するの初めてだ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560586,
      "updated": 1780560592
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21358400000000004d4087",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561274,
      "updated": 1780561274
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21358400000000004d4088",
      "text": "うまくいった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561274,
      "updated": 1780561280
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21358600000000004d4089",
      "text": " [/takker/V1 Road map for scrapbox-userscript-std]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561278,
      "updated": 1780561278
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360000000000004d4090",
      "text": " code:final-report.md",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561399,
      "updated": 1780561418
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4091",
      "text": "  ページの更新が完了しました！",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4092",
      "text": "  cosense-cli（@helpfeel/cosense-cli）を使って、scrapbox.io/takker の「V1 Road map for scrapbox-userscript-std」ページを編集しました。",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4093",
      "text": "  更新内容のサマリー",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4094",
      "text": "  V1項目に達成済みマーク（✅）を付加：",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4095",
      "text": "  - deno.jsonc で組み込み型定義を決める",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4096",
      "text": "  - <reference no-default-lib=\"true\" /> を一掃する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4097",
      "text": "  - jsr.io に publish する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4098",
      "text": "  - option-t の導入",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d4099",
      "text": "  - いらない関数・動いていない関数の削除",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409a",
      "text": "  - scrapbox-userscript-websocket の統合",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409b",
      "text": "  - jsr への publish",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409c",
      "text": "  新規追加「今後の方針（post-V1）」セクション：",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409d",
      "text": "  1. throwの撲滅 — browser/dom/ や api/、websocket/ に残っている throw を Result 型に置き換える",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409e",
      "text": "  2. unstable-apiの統合・安定化 — rest/ と api/ で重複・分断している機能を統合し、一貫した Result 型のエラー処理にする",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d409f",
      "text": "  3. test coverage の向上 — browser/dom/ と websocket/、api/ のテストを追加する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a0",
      "text": "  4. examples/ の作成 — README から参照しているが未作成の examples/ ディレクトリを整備する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a1",
      "text": "  5. Node.js サポートの安定化 — npm ビルドの型チェック有効化とテスト実行を目指す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a2",
      "text": "  編集URL",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a3",
      "text": "  https://scrapbox.io/takker/V1_Road_map_for_scrapbox-userscript-std",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a4",
      "text": "  補足：cosense-cliの認証設定",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a5",
      "text": "  認証に最初失敗した原因は settings.json の形式でした。cosense-cliが期待するのは以下の形式です：",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a6",
      "text": "  {",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a7",
      "text": "    \"users\": [",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a8",
      "text": "      {",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40a9",
      "text": "        \"url\": \"https://scrapbox.io\",",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40aa",
      "text": "        \"token\": \"pat_xxxxxxxx\"",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40ab",
      "text": "      }",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40ac",
      "text": "    ],",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40ad",
      "text": "    \"projects\": []",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40ae",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21360200000000004d40af",
      "text": "  origins キーではなく users 配列に token を入れる必要がありました。修正後、無事認証が通りました。",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561401,
      "updated": 1780561401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21359b00000000004d408a",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/ae56c1293eda4bed643516f459a5fd40]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561297,
      "updated": 1780561297
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2135bd00000000004d408d",
      "text": " [日付リンク]を入れるスタイルを察してくれたみたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561331,
      "updated": 1780561345
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21359b00000000004d408b",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/f580ad69619573726adc63918ce8455b]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561297,
      "updated": 1780561348
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2135dd00000000004d408f",
      "text": "  今回の場合は箇条書きちゃんと入ったみたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561363,
      "updated": 1780561370
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2135bb00000000004d408c",
      "text": "内容はともかく、書き込めることはわかった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561330,
      "updated": 1780561438
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21364c00000000004d40b0",
      "text": " OpenCode非対応であっても、Kimiの問題解決能力が高いので、心配しなくてもうまいこと動かしてくれた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561475,
      "updated": 1780561505
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2132dd00000000004d4082",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560596,
      "updated": 1780560596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2132dd00000000004d4083",
      "text": "やりたいこと",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560596,
      "updated": 1780560599
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2132e000000000004d4084",
      "text": " [/scrapbox-userscript-std]を[KarpathyのLLM Wiki]にする",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560599,
      "updated": 1780560623
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2132fb00000000004d4085",
      "text": "  [/nishio/LLM WikiをScrapboxスタイルに]を参考にする？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560626,
      "updated": 1780560670
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21332800000000004d4086",
      "text": "  これは既存のLLM Wikiをscrapboxにするときの方法だから違うか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560670,
      "updated": 1780560681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a21309000000000004d406e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780560007,
      "updated": 1780560007
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134a40000000000285f5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561060,
      "updated": 1780561060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134a40000000000285f5d",
      "text": "from [2026/06/04#6a21346700000000009a047e][terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561060,
      "updated": 1780561064
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134a80000000000285f5f",
      "text": "\t箇条書きがうまく入らない？",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561065,
      "updated": 1780561073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134b10000000000285f60",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/4b3924a41871ace00c66d7c3729011a7]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561073,
      "updated": 1780561080
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134b80000000000285f61",
      "text": "\tこうなって欲しかった（手で直した）",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561080,
      "updated": 1780563827
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2134bf0000000000285f62",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/bf9ac62a6146126f6ce15cb09ee45105]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561088,
      "updated": 1780561091
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2136d70000000000285f64",
      "text": "\t\t[- 自分で記法を変換させなきゃということか。]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780561623,
      "updated": 1780564884
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2143940000000000ce8896",
      "text": "\t\t文脈引き継がないやつでもう一度同じことさせたらちゃんと箇条書きになった。なんだったんだ、さっきのは。実行前のお祈りが足りなかったのかな。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1780564885,
      "updated": 1780564958
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2144c20000000000b3bbcd",
      "text": "\t\tモデルでも変わるかも？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780565176,
      "updated": 1780565181
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2144cf0000000000b3bbce",
      "text": "\t\t あとはskillの内容を把握できているかどうか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780565191,
      "updated": 1780565202
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2135d100000000004d408e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780561352,
      "updated": 1780561352
    }
  ]
}